## 📦 Dataset layout

The repository expects data in a structure like:

```text
data/
└── LRS3/
    ├── <client_or_identity_id>/
    │   ├── 50001.mp4
    │   ├── 50001.txt
    │   ├── 50002.mp4
    │   └── 50002.txt
    └── ...
```

For dataset preparation details, read:
- `data/README_DATA.md`
- `docs/dataset_preparation.md`

